features: √ 3-LEVEL VOLUME LIMITER FOR HEARING PROTECTION WITH SAFE VOLUME: Kid headphones adopt exclusive proprietary 3-level volume limiter(75dB/85dB/94dB) to protect vulnerable and sensitive ears while give parents a piece of mind, not having to constantly monitor the volume. It can effectively protect children of different ages from progressive hearing loss in different environments. (75/85dB in quiet places or 94dB in noisy surroundings). Two superior speakers provide crystal clear sound.
√ BUILT IN MIC: Kids headset with microphone allows hands free talking,let you pick up calls and skip between tracks in playlist without missing a beat.

√ FOLDABLE AND DURABLE HEADPHONES WIRED: The adjustable headband with memory stainless steel strips gives this headphone some impressive flexibility and durability. 4.9FT/1.5M premium braided nylon fabric audio cable.

√ SHARING JACK: No need for a splitter. Kids can have another headphone plug into the sharing jack on the left side of the headphone to share audio with friends or families. Compatible with Chromebook, Amazon Fire Tablet, Switch, Smartphone, Laptop and all 3.5mm audio jack device.

√ EASY CARRYING & SATISFYING SERVICE: Folding and compact design convenient in carrying and storage.Kids can easily fold them up and put them into the carrying pouch for Airplane, travel and school. You’re entitled to enjoy 24-hour Customer-friendly Support Service. Any question please feel hassle-free to contact us.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Simolio has been focusing on the research and application of hearing technology in audio products, esp in hearing protection and TV hearing assistance products, to help people protect their hearing as well as get more enjoyable listening experiences. As a professional supplier in the field of wireless TV hearing assistance products, our products have won good reputation for helping thousands of people with hearing impairment in US market. Welcome to visit Simolio Direct storefront for researching other products. In the meantime, we found that many people, especially children are used to listen to loud sounds without volume limited from various normal headphones which usually make the ears being hurt unconsciously, even some expensive adult headphones which have complex sound technology and no limit to volume that can also cause children's hearing loss for long time loudly listening. Therefore, in addition to providing audio products for the seniors or people with hearing loss to help them clearly listen to TV programs/music, we are paying more attention to the healthy growth of children. We have been developing the Simolio Kid's Hearing Protection Headphones series, hoping to protect every children from progressive hearing loss and let moms feel at ease. We hope that our products will make your family happy and care for your children.

In-Line Mic The 3.5mm tangle-free nylon braided audio cable built-in HD microphone enables clear, hands-free communications, let you pick up calls and skip between tracks in playlist without missing a beat. Built-in Share Port - Make Kids Learn to Share Designed with 3.5mm AUX share port on the left side of the headphone allows another headphone to connect with, kids can share their favorite music or movies with their friends or families at school or home, on travelling or flying. Flexible & Durable & Adjustable The headband with memory stainless steel strips give the headphones some impressive durability and flexibility. It can withstand the kids’ restless hands, no need to worry about being broken easily from pulling or bending. The ear pads won't fall off easily by using some nifty engineering. Lightweight, free to adjust, can fit children of different ages. Compact & Foldable Each headphone comes in cute portable pouch, making it a perfect gift for birthdays, holidays and more!

Compatible with all devices that enabled a 3.5mm stereo output, including iPod, Phone, Android smartphones and tablets, laptop etc. No matter you are in train or subway or on plane, this headphone will add a lot of joy and fun. Perfect for children to use at school for computer lab or do some online coursework.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 16, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exceptional customer service
reviews.reviewText: The first set I ordered didn't work properly. One side had very low sound. I contacted them and received a response immediately and they sent a new pair. Fantastic customer service. The headphones are great for my child. They work wonderfully, fit her head well and even has a port so when she actually does share, she can share with her silblings.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My granddaughter loves them! They fit well, are light, and flexible. Great for her tablet and Chrome book!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2021
reviews.reviewText: *Update* Customer service was great. They sent a new pair of headphones. These headphones look nicely made, just like the others I ordered. They have great sound and volume control. I like the nylon cord as well. I do hope that these ones last us much longer than the other pair. I’m glad that customer service was so responsive. I’d buy from them again. I only gave 4 stars because of the other pair of headphones dying so quickly.I thought I was getting better quality headphones for the kids. They are flexible, have mic, and great volume control. My kids said they’re very comfortable too. My child used them twice before they stopped working. Like any typical cheaply made headphone. Will be returning. Disappointed

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy with the purchase
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my granddaughter for kindergarten. She loves it and so do I. It is a really great product worth the cost. I love how it bends and doesn't break, very necessary for a child her age. Volume and sound are great and regulated, so she doesn't hurt her eardrums. Also, great that a other person can connect to listen on at same time. The ear pads are perfect fitting her small ears.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are genius
reviews.reviewText: While at my kid's swim meet (which can be loooong with big breaks in-between when you're swimmer is competing), I saw a family in front of us with 3 kids all watching the same tablet. Made possible because the headphones all connected into each other and then into the tablet.GENIUS.So I asked where they got them and was directed to these on Amazon. I got 3 pairs in preparation for a long flight for my kids. This made it possible for multiple kids to watch a movie on the same tablet. Fewer fights/complaints. My kids loved them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great product for the money! This is the 3rd one I have purchased (the other 2 were destroyed by the other parent) love the color on these and they hold up very well to the abuse of my children
